<h2 id="list管理">List管理</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Directory: _featured_tags
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>在文件夹中添加文件，头部格式</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>---
layout: list
title: [content]
slug: [tag] #用于链接到该list的文件
menu: true
order: num
description: &gt;
  content
accent_color: '#268bd2'
accent_image:
  background: '#202020'
  overlay:    false
---
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="post管理">Post管理</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Direcoty: _posts
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>在文件夹中添加文件，头部格式如下</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>---
layout: post
title: Archlinux install
description: &gt;
  Content
tags: [tag] #对应上面的tag
author: zcy
---
</code></pre></div></div>

